<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Solicitud de invitación · Paso 2 · TuDiaEspecial</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-logo">TuDia<span>Especial</span></div>
  </nav>

  <section style="padding-top:120px;padding-bottom:80px;background:var(--warm-white);">
    <div class="section-header" style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto 40px;">
      <span class="section-label">Formulario · Paso 2 de 2</span>
    </div>

    <form action="/solicitud/paso2/<%= order.id %>" method="post" style="max-width:740px;margin:0 auto;background:var(--offwhite);padding:32px 24px;border-radius:4px;border:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:var(--shadow-soft);display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:18px 24px;">
      
      <!-- Elección de plantilla -->
      <div style="grid-column:1 / -1;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:12px;">Elegí tu plantilla</h3>
        
        <div style="margin-top:16px;padding:16px;background:rgba(212,175,55,0.1);border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.2);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink);">
          <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:20px;list-style-type:disc;">
            <li style="margin-bottom:8px;">Las plantillas son solo sugerencias de colores, tipografías y formatos. Todo se puede modificar, comentándolo por WhatsApp o Instagram antes o después de la entrega.</li>
            <li>Enviar las imágenes y cualquier detalle por WhatsApp o Instagram luego de realizar el pedido.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <style>
          .carousel-section {
            position: relative;
            margin: 0 -24px;
            padding: 0 24px;
          }
          .carousel-container {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
          }
          .carousel-track {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            -ms-overflow-style: none;
            scrollbar-width: none;
            padding: 4px 0;
          }
          .carousel-track::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
          }
          .carousel-item {
            flex: 0 0 280px;
            position: relative;
          }
          .template-preview-title {
            font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;
            font-size:0.9rem;
            font-weight:500;
            text-align:center;
            margin-bottom:8px;
            color:var(--ink);
          }
          .template-preview-card {
            position: relative;
            border:2px solid var(--border);
            border-radius:8px;
            overflow:hidden;
            background:var(--offwhite);
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
          }
          .template-preview-image {
            width:100%;
            height:100%;
            object-fit:cover;
          }
          .template-preview-placeholder {
            display:none;
            padding:40px 20px;
            text-align:center;
            font-size:0.85rem;
            color:var(--muted);
          }
          .carousel-nav {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: var(--gold);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50%;
            font-size: 24px;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 10;
            color: var(--ink);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
          }
          .carousel-nav:hover {
            background: #d4af37;
          }
          .carousel-prev {
            left: 8px;
          }
          .carousel-next {
            right: 8px;
          }
          .selected-template-text {
            margin-top: 16px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            background: rgba(212,175,55,0.1);
            border: 1px solid var(--gold);
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-align: center;
            font-family:'Jost',sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--ink);
          }
          .selected-template-text strong {
            color: var(--gold);
            font-weight: 600;
          }
          .selected-template-text a {
            color: var(--link);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-style: italic;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: block;
          }
          .selected-template-text a:hover {
            color: var(--gold);
          }
          @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .carousel-nav {
              width: 32px;
              height: 32px;
              font-size: 18px;
            }
          }
          /* Estilo para plantilla seleccionada */
          input[type="radio"]:checked + .template-preview-card {
            border-color: var(--gold);
            border-width: 4px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(212,175,55,0.4), 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
          }
        </style>
        
        <% if (order.category === 'bodas') { %>
        <div class="carousel-section">
          <div class="carousel-container">
            <button type="button" class="carousel-nav carousel-prev" onclick="moveCarousel('bodas', -1)">‹</button>
            <button type="button" class="carousel-nav carousel-next" onclick="moveCarousel('bodas', 1)">›</button>
            <div class="carousel-track" id="bodas-track">
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <h4 class="template-preview-title">Boda Minimal</h4>
                <label style="cursor:pointer;display:block;">
                  <input type="radio" name="template_key" value="boda_minimal" required style="position:absolute;opacity:0;">
                  <div class="template-preview-card">
                    <img src="/images/templates/mocksTemplates/BodaMinimal.jpg" alt="Boda Minimal Template" class="template-preview-image" onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
                    <div class="template-preview-placeholder">Imagen no disponible</div>
                  </div>
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <h4 class="template-preview-title">Boda Midnight</h4>
                <label style="cursor:pointer;display:block;">
                  <input type="radio" name="template_key" value="boda_midnight" style="position:absolute;opacity:0;">
                  <div class="template-preview-card">
                    <img src="/images/templates/mocksTemplates/BodaMidnight.png" alt="Boda Midnight Template" class="template-preview-image" onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
                    <div class="template-preview-placeholder">Imagen no disponible</div>
                  </div>
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <h4 class="template-preview-title">Boda Garden</h4>
